<p>20/11/17<br/>news of a battle near Heligoland nothing definite</p>
<p>21/11/17<br/>Raining since the night of 20/11/17 of &amp; on  The ice cream vendors by the reports are giving the sausage eaters a go for their trouble.  Plenty of German talk about General Smuts being a succesor to Lloyd George</p>
<p>23/11/17<br/>Talk about Russian asking for a seperate peace.  Bitterly cold today.</p>
<p>24/11/17<br/>Rain today of &amp; on.  news of British advance upon Cambre.  see by reports they have taken at last Reincourt where our Brigade or what was left rather were captured 11/4/7</p>
<p>25/11/17<br/>Letters today one from [indecipherable] none from home.  letters handed out on parade</p>
<p>26/11/17<br/>Snow this morning beautiful</p>
